Dear Sir / Madam,

My name is Mrs. Fatemeh Ani from Iran, I got your email contact from online
website. I am the Regional Manager of Iranian Offshore Engineering and
Construction Company. I want to start a Business Enterprise in your country
and I would like you to assist me, Please reply to discuss further. Thank
you.

Best Regards,
Mrs. Fatemeh Ani.
Regional Manager,
Iranian Offshore Engineering and Construction Company.
